msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/complete"
msgid "Congratulations, you have finished the third tutorial (AT guns and artillery)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/date"
msgid "June 24th, 1941 · Border with the USSR"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/hint_video"
msgid "Press this button to re-watch the video for this tutorial phase."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/name"
msgid "Tutorial 3: AT Guns and Artillery"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/name_big"
msgid "AT Guns and Artillery"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/00"
msgid "Soldaten! Welcome back to the front line! Today you will learn how to deploy Anti-Tank guns, build sandbags, and distinguish between direct and indirect fire units."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/01"
msgid "First, use all of your soldiers to crew the Anti-Tank gun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/01b"
msgid "Soldiers, it's time to relocate the AT gun to a new firing position near the pond. Move it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/02"
msgid "Great! Now it's time to build sandbags around your AT gun for extra protection!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/03"
msgid "Enemy vehicles down the road! Wipe them out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/04"
msgid "What is this?! It's a heavy Soviet tank, a KV-1! Take it out immediately using APCR rounds!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/04b"
msgid "Great job destroying the heavy tank! Now let us prepare to relocate again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/05"
msgid "Here, take this truck and attach your AT gun to it so you can tow it quickly to a new location."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/05b"
msgid "Detach the AT gun and move it into position near the trenches!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/06a"
msgid "Now we will familiarize ourselves with our standard light field howitzer, the 10.5cm LeFH 18! First, you need some ammunition for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/06b"
msgid "You now possess an ammunition truck. Crew the artillery piece and drive the truck closer to resupply your howitzer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/07"
msgid "Soviets have arrived at the village west of our location. Use the howitzer to destroy their trucks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/07helper"
msgid "Firing multiple shots at the same target or location increases the accuracy of each subsequent shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/08"
msgid "Soviets armored car spotted! Switch the howitzer ammunition to either armor-piercing (APHE) or high-explosive anti-tank (HEAT) to destroy it with direct fire!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/ger_officer/09"
msgid "An exceptional kill! Now, kill the remaining enemy soldiers!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/hint/01"
msgid "Your AT gun is set to 'return fire' firing mode. Switch to 'fire at will' or manually shoot in direct control mode."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/01"
msgid "This is the 5cm PaK 38. It is a direct-fire Anti-Tank weapon. Ideal for ambushing enemy tanks with pinpoint accuracy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/02"
msgid "Changing your location is always good idea. For example, your new location should allow for an even better angle of the road."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/narrator/scene/03"
msgid "Tow your AT gun to the new position using the truck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/outro_completed"
msgid "Mission Accomplished!\n\n"
"Click on 'continue' to keep playing this mission or click on 'next' to proceed directly into the next mission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/place"
msgid "Army Group Centre"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/reinf_video"
msgid "Re-watch steps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/replay_video"
msgid "Replay Video"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/story"
msgid "Welcome to artillery training, Soldier.\n\n"
"In this tutorial you will learn the basics of artillery emplacements and how their direct and indirect fire modes can be decisive in battle.\n\n"
"What artillery lacks in mobility, it makes up for in firepower.\n\n"
"                                        Good luck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task1"
msgid "Crew the AT gun with all your men."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task1b"
msgid "Move your AT gun to a new location as shown."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task2"
msgid "Build sandbags for your AT gun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task3"
msgid "Destroy the enemy vehicles!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task4"
msgid "Destroy the enemy KV-1!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5a"
msgid "Connect your AT gun to the truck for towing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5"
msgid "Tow the AT gun to the new position as indicated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task5b"
msgid "Detach the AT gun and move it into the given position."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task6"
msgid "Resupply the light field howitzer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task7"
msgid "Destroy the enemy trucks with the howitzer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task8"
msgid "Destroy the Soviet armored car with direct fire with AP/HEAT shells."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/task9"
msgid "Destroy the remaining enemy units."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/03_artillery-reinforcements/outro_failed"
msgid "You have been defeated!"
msgstr ""